                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "The G4GC is generally considered a very reliable and robust engine. Its naturally aspirated, MPI design is inherently simple and durable. The main long-term consideration is the critical timing belt replacement at 90,000 km. With proper maintenance, including regular oil changes and timely replacement of wear items like ignition coils, it can easily exceed 200,000 km.",
