                    text: "Significant power gains are limited due to its naturally aspirated design. Basic ECU remapping can yield minor improvements (5-10 kW), but substantial increases require forced induction (turbo/supercharger), which is complex and expensive. Bolt-on modifications like intake and exhaust offer minimal gains.",
