                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "Official combined figures are around 8.5 L/100km (33 mpg UK) for the Sephia. Real-world economy typically ranges from 9.5-11.5 L/100km (25-30 mpg UK) for mixed driving, which was competitive for its era and class.",
