                    text: "Generally very reliable with proper maintenance. Its main long-term consideration is the timing chain tensioner, which can wear and cause a rattle on cold starts after high mileage. Addressing this with a tensioner replacement ensures continued smooth operation. The engine is known for its durability and low running costs.",
