                    text: "The most frequent issues are timing chain tensioner wear causing a cold-start rattle, potential VVT solenoid failure leading to performance issues, and engine mount deterioration causing vibration. Coolant thermostat failures are also occasionally reported. These are documented in Kia service information.",
